  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 400 degrees Fahrenheit.",
    "In a large bowl, whisk together olive oil, lemon juice, garlic powder, cumin powder, paprika, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Add the chicken wings to the bowl and toss to coat with the marinade.",
    "Line a baking sheet with aluminum foil and spray with cooking spray.",
    "Arrange the chicken wings on the baking sheet in a single layer.",
    "Sprinkle the bonito flakes over the chicken wings.",
    "Bake the chicken wings for 30 minutes or until cooked through.",
    "Garnish with chopped fresh parsley and serve hot.",
    "Serve with a side of Turkish rice or salad for a complete meal."
